videos.description: Bowling Green comes out hot and takes the early 10 point lead after Scott Miller hauls in the 6 yard TD.
videos.headline: Bowling Green WR hauls in TD for 10-0 lead

videos.description: On 4th-and-14 Justin Herbert finds Jaylon Redd for the 33-yard TD cutting Bowling Green's lead to 3.
videos.headline: Justin Herbert fires dart for fourth-down TD

videos.description: Justin Herbert rolls to his right and fires a laser to Dillon Mitchell in the back of the end zone for the Ducks' TD.
videos.headline: Herbert rolls right and finds Mitchell for Oregon TD

videos.description: Oregon's Justin Hollins knocks the ball loose and it is recovered by Jalen Jelks. The Ducks capitalized with a TD a few plays later.
videos.headline: Oregon's defense recovers fumble

videos.description: Oregon's Johnny Johnson III hauls in the pass and drags defenders into the end zone for the TD.
videos.headline: Oregon WR hauls in pass and fights his way for TD

videos.description: Oregon safety Ugochukwu Amadi gets the interception and returns it 38 yards for the TD.
videos.headline: Oregon safety able to get the pick-6

videos.description: Oregon RB Taj Griffin catches the short pass, then shows off the jets for an 83-yard TD.
videos.headline: Oregon RB breaks free for 83-yard TD catch

videos.description: Bowling Green WR Scott Miller catches and runs for 63 yards converting his 2nd TD of the day.
videos.headline: Bowling Green WR hauls in 63-yard catch for TD
